{"id": 4092, "title": "Ticket #4092: add support for config from url to windows installer", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn order for CHTC to install HTCondor in CSL and Doit Windows desktops, they need a way to tell the MSI installer to pull local config from a URL. HTCondor can currently do this using the pipe config, but Windows has no native command line tool for fetching from a URL, and the MSI installer doesn't know how to set LOCAL_CONFIG_FILE.\n\n<p>We need to address both of these issues.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2013-Nov-27 16:05:05 by johnkn:</em> <br/>\n\nsome of the code is done for 8.1.3, but not all of it. target for 8.1.5</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-May-29 09:52</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/a6e96d49803d4dad6430beb531b94d64fc71e593\">[40264]</a></span>: minor edit of new doc <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4092\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('4092'); return false;\" title=\"add support for config from url to windows installer\">#4092</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2014-May-28 14:36</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/ec18437c297a44ad724085f4466f018d77d73605\">[40246]</a></span>: documentation for config-from-url in windows installer <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=4092\" onclick